  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve][Takuya Kanbara]: Cost 2 [Digivolve][BurningGreymon]:
    Cost 1 \n\nYou may digivolve this card from your hand onto one of your red Tamers
    as if that card is a level 3 red Digimon.\n[When Digivolving] If [BurningGreymon]
    is in this Digimon's digivolution cards or you have a blue or green Digimon or
    Tamer, this Digimon may digivolve into [AncientGreymon] in the hand for a digivolution
    cost of 3, ignoring its digivolution requirements. If digivolved by this effect,
    delete this Digimon at the end of the turn."
